<inglise> Claims arising out of transactions in connection with which a criminal conviction has been obtained for money laundering, as defined in Article 1 of Council Directive 91/308/EEC of 10 June 1991 on prevention of the use of the financial system for the purpose of money laundering (10), shall be excluded from any compensation under investor-compensation schemes. </inglise>
<eesti> N&otilde;uded, mis tulenevad tehingutest, millega seoses on tehtud s&uuml;&uuml;dim&otilde;istev kohtuotsus rahapesu eest n&otilde;ukogu 10. juuni 1991. aasta rahanduss&uuml;steemi rahapesuks kasutamise v&auml;ltimist k&auml;sitleva direktiivi 91/308/EM&Uuml; artiklis 1 m&auml;&auml;ratletud t&auml;henduses, ei saa investeeringute tagamise skeemide kohast h&uuml;vitist. </eesti>
