<inglise> Article 5 </inglise>
<eesti> Artikkel 5 </eesti>
<inglise> 1. </inglise>
<eesti> 1. </eesti>
<inglise> If an investment firm required by Article 2 (1) to belong to a scheme does not meet the obligations incumbent on it as a member of that scheme, the competent authorities which issued its authorization shall be notified and, in cooperation with the compensation scheme, shall take all measures appropriate, including the imposition of penalties, to ensure that the investment firm meets its obligations. </inglise>
<eesti> Kui investeerimis&uuml;hing, kes peab artikli 2 l&otilde;ike 1 kohaselt kuuluma skeemi, ei t&auml;ida tal selle skeemi liikmena lasuvaid kohustusi, teatatakse sellest investeerimis&uuml;hingule tegevusloa v&auml;ljastanud p&auml;devatele asutustele, kes v&otilde;tavad koost&ouml;&ouml;s tagatisskeemiga k&otilde;ik vajalikud meetmed, sealhulgas sanktsioonide kehtestamine, tagamaks, et investeerimis&uuml;hing t&auml;idab oma kohustused. </eesti>
<inglise> 2. </inglise>
<eesti> 2. </eesti>
<inglise> If those measures fail to secure compliance on the part of the investment firm, the scheme may, where national law permits the exclusion of a member, with the express consent of the competent authorities, give not less than 12 months' notice of its intention of excluding the investment firm from membership of the scheme. </inglise>
<eesti> Kui need meetmed ei taga, et investeerimis&uuml;hing t&auml;idab oma kohustused, v&otilde;ib skeem, kui siseriiklik &otilde;igus lubab liiget v&auml;lja arvata, p&auml;devate asutuste selges&otilde;nalisel n&otilde;usolekul teatada v&auml;hemalt 12 kuud ette oma kavatsusest investeerimis&uuml;hing s&uuml;steemist v&auml;lja arvata. </eesti>
<inglise> The scheme shall continue to provide cover under the second subparagraph of Article 2 (2) in respect of investment business transacted during that period. </inglise>
<eesti> S&uuml;steem pakub artikli 2 l&otilde;ike 2 teise l&otilde;igu kohast kaitset ka k&otilde;nealusel ajavahemikul toimunud investeerimistegevusele. </eesti>
<inglise> If, on expiry of the period of notice, the investment firm has not met its obligations, the compensation scheme may, again having obtained the express consent of the competent authorities, exclude it. </inglise>
<eesti> Kui etteteatamist&auml;htaja m&ouml;&ouml;dumisel ei ole investeerimis&uuml;hing oma kohustusi t&auml;itnud, v&otilde;ib tagatisskeem p&auml;rast p&auml;devate asutuste selges&otilde;nalise n&otilde;usoleku saamist &uuml;hingu v&auml;lja arvata. </eesti>
<inglise> 3. </inglise>
<eesti> 3. </eesti>
<inglise> Where national law permits, and with the express consent of the competent authorities which issued its authorization, an investment firm excluded from an investor-compensation scheme may continue to provide investment services if, before its exclusion, it made alternative compensation arrangements which ensure that investors will enjoy cover that is at least equivalent to that offered by the officially recognized scheme and has characteristics equivalent to those of that scheme. </inglise>
<eesti> Kui siseriiklik &otilde;igus seda lubab ja tegevusloa v&auml;ljastanud p&auml;devad asutused annavad selges&otilde;nalise n&otilde;usoleku, v&otilde;ib investeeringute tagamise skeemist v&auml;ljaarvatud investeerimis&uuml;hing j&auml;tkata investeerimisteenuste osutamist, kui ta seadis enne oma v&auml;ljaarvamist sisse m&otilde;ne muu h&uuml;vitamiskorra, mis tagab, et investoritele pakutav kaitse on v&auml;hemalt v&otilde;rdv&auml;&auml;rne ametlikult tunnustatud skeemi pakutavaga ja selle omadused on samav&auml;&auml;rsed k&otilde;nealuse skeemi omadega. </eesti>
<inglise> 4. </inglise>
<eesti> 4. </eesti>
<inglise> If an investment firm the exclusion of which is proposed under paragraph 2 is unable to make alternative arrangements which comply with the conditions imposed in paragraph 3, the competent authorities which issued its authorization shall withdraw it forthwith. </inglise>
<eesti> Kui investeerimis&uuml;hing, kelle v&auml;ljaarvamiseks on tehtud ettepanek l&otilde;ike 2 alusel, ei suuda sisse seada m&otilde;nda muud korda, mis vastab l&otilde;ikes 3 kehtestatud tingimustele, t&uuml;histavad tegevusloa v&auml;ljastanud p&auml;devad ametiasutused selle tegevusloa viivitamata. </eesti>
<inglise> Article 6 </inglise>
<eesti> Artikkel 6 </eesti>
<inglise> After the withdrawal of an investment firm's authorization, cover under the second subparagraph of Article 2 (2) shall continue to be provided in respect of investment business transacted up to the time of that withdrawal. </inglise>
