<inglise> Article 7 </inglise>
<eesti> Artikkel 7 </eesti>
<inglise> 1. </inglise>
<eesti> 1. </eesti>
<inglise> Investor-compensation schemes introduced and officially recognized in a Member State in accordance with Article 2 (1) shall also cover investors at branches set up by investment firms in other Member States. </inglise>
